<subSubSection id="C3132FECFFF0FFFDFF34B704EFFA0295" pageId="0" pageNumber="297" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BB67C67FFF0FFFDFF34B704EFFA0295" blockId="0.[136,1452,1356,1706]" pageId="0" pageNumber="297">
Etymology:—The specific epithet is derived from the prefix 
<emphasis id="B97DA075FFF0FFFDFCA1B705EC680271" box="[797,836,1611,1634]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="297">neo</emphasis>
-, meaning new, and 
<taxonomicName id="4C0907E4FFF0FFFDFB94B704EBBD0271" authorityName="E. W. Berry" authorityYear="1916" box="[1064,1169,1610,1634]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Celastraceae" genus="Euonymus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Celastrales" pageId="0" pageNumber="297" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="splendens">
<emphasis id="B97DA075FFF0FFFDFB94B704EBBD0271" box="[1064,1169,1610,1634]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="297">splendens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the epithet of 
<bibRefCitation id="EF980196FFF0FFFDFA8BB704EA800271" author="Averyanov, L. V." box="[1335,1452,1610,1634]" pageId="0" pageNumber="297" pagination="1 - 431" refId="ref808" refString="Averyanov, L. V. (2019) Rosaceae. In: Averyanov, L. V., Nguyen, K. S., Maisak, T. (Eds.) Plant diversity, flora and vegetation of Hin Nam No National Protected Area: Plant Communities and Plant Species Diversity of Hin Nam No National Protected Area. Lap Lambert Academic Publishing, pp. 1 - 431." type="book chapter" year="2019">Averyanov</bibRefCitation>
(2019).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
